            <div class="quote-case-name">La Bella Pandita</div>
            <div class="quote-case-desc">De 1 tienda piloto a 42 sucursales sincronizadas en 3 años.</div>
            <div class="quote-case-metrics">
              <span><strong>+300%</strong> lifetime value</span>
              <span><strong>45%</strong> clientes leales</span>
            </div>
            <div class="quote-case-quote">"Dejamos de ser solo retail físico para convertirnos en una operación omnicanal integrada."</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="quote-case-card">
          <img src="/images/case-casa-maca.webp" alt="Casa Maca" class="quote-case-img" width="400" height="240" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="quote-case-body">
            <div class="quote-case-tag" style="background:#E8A838;color:#1a1a1a">Moda consciente</div>
            <div class="quote-case-name">Casa Maca</div>
            <div class="quote-case-desc">Moda sustentable desde Guadalajara. 2 boutiques + e-commerce + social commerce conectados.</div>
            <div class="quote-case-metrics">
              <span><strong>-80%</strong> trabajo manual</span>
              <span><strong>+25%</strong> ticket promedio</span>
            </div>
            <div class="quote-case-quote">"Casa Maca diseña desde la intuición, pero ahora opera con datos."</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-cases-dots" id="cases-dots">
        <button class="quote-cases-dot active" data-idx="0"></button>
        <button class="quote-cases-dot" data-idx="1"></button>
        <button class="quote-cases-dot" data-idx="2"></button>
      </div>
    </div>
    </section>
    )}

    {/* Legal — vive dentro del tab Firmar y aceptar */}
    <section class="quote-tab-panel" data-tab="firma">
    <div class="quote-legal">
      Al aceptar esta cotización, confirmas que has leído y aceptas nuestros <a href="https://www.sacscloud.com/terminos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Términos y condiciones</a> y nuestro <a href="https://www.sacscloud.com/privacidad" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Aviso de privacidad</a>.
    </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer (always visible) -->
    <div class="quote-footer">
      <div class="quote-footer-brand">
        <span class="quote-footer-logo">Sacs</span>
        <span class="quote-footer-tagline">Sistema operativo para retailers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-footer-contact">
        www.sacscloud.com · administracion@sacscloud.com
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Actions (hidden in print) -->
  <div class="quote-actions no-print">
    {quote.estado === 'accepted' && (
      <div class="quote-accepted-badge">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        Cotización aceptada {quote.aceptado_por ? `por ${quote.aceptado_por}` : ''}
      </div>
    )}
    {isExpired && !isClosed ? (
      <div class="quote-expired-notice">
        <div class="quote-expired-notice-title">Esta cotización ha vencido</div>
        <div class="quote-expired-notice-text">Los precios y condiciones ya no son vigentes. Contactanos para recibir una cotización actualizada.</div>
        <a class="quote-action-btn" href={`https://wa.me/5215512345678?text=${encodeURIComponent(`Hola, la cotización ${quote.numero} venció. Me gustaría recibir una cotización actualizada.`)}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Solicitar recotización</a>
      </div>
    ) : (
      <div class="quote-actions-row">
        <button class="quote-action-btn" id="btn-comments">Realizar comentarios</button>
        <button class="quote-action-btn" id="btn-share">Compartir por correo</button>
        <button class="quote-action-btn" onclick="window.print()">Descargar PDF</button>
      </div>
    )}
  </div>

  <!-- Comments modal -->
  <div class="quote-modal-overlay no-print" id="comments-section" style="display:none">
    <div class="quote-modal">
      <div class="quote-modal-header">
        <span class="quote-modal-title">Comentarios</span>
        <button class="quote-modal-close" id="btn-close-comments">✕</button>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-comments-thread" id="comments-thread">
        <div class="quote-comments-empty" id="comments-empty">Sin comentarios aun. Escribe tu primera pregunta o solicitud.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-modal-footer">
        <input type="text" id="comment-name" placeholder="Tu nombre" class="quote-modal-input" />
        <textarea id="comment-text" placeholder="Escribe tu comentario, pregunta o solicitud..." class="quote-modal-input" rows="3"></textarea>
        <button class="quote-modal-btn" id="btn-send-comment">Enviar comentario</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Share modal -->
  <div class="quote-modal-overlay no-print" id="share-section" style="display:none">
    <div class="quote-modal">
      <div class="quote-modal-header">
        <span class="quote-modal-title">Compartir por correo</span>
        <button class="quote-modal-close" id="btn-close-share">✕</button>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-modal-body">
        <p class="quote-modal-hint">Envia esta cotización a alguien mas. Se abrira tu cliente de correo con el link incluido.</p>
        <div class="quote-share-grid">
          <div>
            <label class="quote-share-label">Para</label>
            <input type="email" id="share-to" placeholder="correo@ejemplo.com" class="quote-modal-input" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="quote-share-label">Tu nombre</label>
            <input type="text" id="share-from" placeholder="Tu nombre" class="quote-modal-input" value={quote.contacto || ''} />
          </div>
          <div style="grid-column:1/-1">
            <label class="quote-share-label">Asunto</label>
            <input type="text" id="share-subject" class="quote-modal-input" value={`Cotización ${quote.numero} — ${quote.empresa}`} />
          </div>
          <div style="grid-column:1/-1">
            <label class="quote-share-label">Mensaje</label>
            <textarea id="share-body" class="quote-modal-input" rows="4">{`Hola,\n\nTe comparto esta cotización para tu revision:\n\nhttps://www.sacscloud.com/cotizacion/${quote.id}\n\nSaludos`}</textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="quote-modal-footer" style="flex-direction:row">
        <button class="quote-modal-btn" id="btn-send-share">Abrir correo</button>
        <button class="quote-modal-btn quote-modal-btn--secondary" onclick="window.print()">Descargar PDF</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
:global(nav), :global(.nav), :global(header), :global(footer), :global(.whatsapp-float) { display: none !important; }

/* 2-column layout: sidebar + content on desktop */
.quote-layout {
  max-width: 1240px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 32px 24px 80px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  gap: 32px;
  align-items: start;
}
.quote-layout-sidebar {
  position: sticky;
  top: 24px;
  max-height: calc(100vh - 48px);
  overflow-y: auto;
  scrollbar-width: thin;
}
.quote-layout-sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
.quote-layout-sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 3px; }
.quote-layout .quote-page { max-width: 100%; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 24px; }

/* Tab anchor: invisible marker, offset to account for scroll-into-view positioning */
.tab-anchor {
  height: 0;
  scroll-margin-top: 24px;
  visibility: hidden;
}

/* Mobile: no sidebar */
@media (max-width: 1023px) {
  .quote-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding: 0 12px 40px;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .quote-layout-sidebar { display: none; }
  .tab-anchor { scroll-margin-top: 130px; }
  .quote-page { padding: 12px 0 60px; }
}

.quote-page { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }
.quote-container { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }

/* ─── Header ─── */
.quote-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; padding: 40px 40px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
.quote-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.quote-client-logo { max-width: 120px; max-height: 48px; width: auto; height: auto; object-fit: contain; }
.quote-logo-text { font-family: var(--font-logo); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; }
.quote-logo-tag { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); background: rgba(75,123,229,0.08); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.quote-meta { text-align: right; }
.quote-number { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; }
.quote-date { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #999; margin-top: 2px; }
.quote-validity { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 600; color: #999; margin-top: 8px; }
.quote-expired { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; color: #E54B4B; margin-top: 8px; }
.quote-paid-banner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 24px; background: #4B7BE5; color: #fff; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; }

/* ─── Status pill (active / expired / accepted / paid) ─── */
.quote-status { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 5px 11px 5px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1; }
.quote-status-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.quote-status--active { background: rgba(153,153,153,0.1); color: #666; }
.quote-status--active .quote-status-dot { background: #999; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(153,153,153,0.12); }
.quote-status--accepted { background: rgba(42,181,160,0.12); color: #1e8471; }
.quote-status--accepted .quote-status-dot { background: #2AB5A0; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(42,181,160,0.18); }
.quote-status--paid { background: rgba(75,123,229,0.12); color: #3764c4; }
.quote-status--paid .quote-status-dot { background: #4B7BE5; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(75,123,229,0.18); }
.quote-status--expired { background: rgba(229,75,75,0.1); color: #b93333; }
.quote-status--expired .quote-status-dot { background: #E54B4B; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(229,75,75,0.15); }
/* Only dim when expired AND not closed (accepted/paid = full opacity, informational only) */
.quote-expired-page .quote-container > *:not(.quote-expired-note):not(.quote-header) { opacity: 0.55; }
.quote-expired-page .quote-container > .quote-header { opacity: 1; }

/* ─── Expired-but-closed note (informational, non-blocking) ─── */
.quote-expired-note { padding: 12px 40px; background: #fafafa; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
.quote-expired-note-label { font-size: 0.625rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; flex-shrink: 0; }
.quote-expired-note-text { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #888; }

/* ─── Tab panel content switcher ─── */
.quote-tab-panel { display: none; animation: tabFade 220ms ease; }
.quote-tab-panel.is-active { display: block; }
@keyframes tabFade { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(4px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .quote-tab-panel { animation: none; }
  .quote-timer-promo-dot { animation: none !important; }
}
/* Constrain tab-panel inner content width on desktop for Squarespace-style breathing room */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .quote-tab-panel > * { max-width: 680px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .quote-tab-panel > .impl-section { max-width: 680px; }
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-timeline-section { max-width: 760px; }
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-table,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-totals,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-tab-cross,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-timer,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-payments,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-bank,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-pay-link,
  .quote-tab-panel > .quote-versions { max-width: 680px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
}

/* ─── Resumen intro tile ─── */
.quote-tab-intro { padding: 56px 56px 48px; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
.quote-tab-intro-eyebrow { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; color: #999; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.quote-tab-intro-heading { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.875rem; font-weight: 300; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.25; letter-spacing: -0.015em; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.quote-tab-intro-total { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; margin-bottom: 32px; }
.quote-tab-intro-total-label { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 600; color: #999; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }
.quote-tab-intro-total-value { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: #1a1a1a; letter-spacing: -0.025em; line-height: 1; }
.quote-tab-intro-total-moneda { font-size: 1rem; color: #999; margin-left: 6px; font-weight: 400; }
.quote-tab-intro-nav { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
.quote-tab-intro-link { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 18px 0; color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5; transition: color 0.15s ease; }
.quote-tab-intro-link:hover { color: #2AB5A0; }
.quote-tab-intro-link-label { font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 500; }
.quote-tab-intro-link-arrow { font-size: 1rem; color: #999; transition: transform 0.15s ease; }
.quote-tab-intro-link:hover .quote-tab-intro-link-arrow { color: #2AB5A0; transform: translateX(4px); }
.quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-heading, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-total-value, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-link { color: #fff; }
.quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-total, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-nav, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-link { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
.quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-eyebrow, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-total-moneda, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-total-label, .quote-dark .quote-tab-intro-link-arrow { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

/* ─── Cross-tab link (e.g., "Ver desglose de pagos →") ─── */
.quote-tab-cross { padding: 0 40px 24px; }
.quote-tab-cross-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #2AB5A0; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; padding-bottom: 2px; transition: border-color 0.15s ease; }
.quote-tab-cross-link:hover { border-color: #2AB5A0; }
.quote-tab-cross-arrow { transition: transform 0.15s ease; }
.quote-tab-cross-link:hover .quote-tab-cross-arrow { transform: translateX(3px); }

/* ─── Closed state (accepted / paid) signed card ─── */
.quote-signed { padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
.quote-signed--closed { padding: 48px 40px; border-top: none; background: #fafafa; }
.quote-signed-eyebrow { font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; color: #2AB5A0; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.quote-signed-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.625rem; font-weight: 300; color: #1a1a1a; letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.quote-signed-sub { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
.quote-signed-img { max-width: 220px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto 12px; display: block; }
.quote-signed-fallback {
  margin: 8px auto 14px;
  padding: 0 0 8px;
  max-width: 280px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
  text-align: center;
}
.quote-signed-fallback span {
  font-family: 'Brush Script MT', 'Lucida Handwriting', 'Apple Chancery', cursive;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 1.875rem;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  display: inline-block;
  transform: rotate(-3deg);
}
.quote-signed-label { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }
.quote-signed-date { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #999; margin-top: 2px; }
.quote-signed-cta { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 14px 32px; background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.875rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em; border-radius: 4px; transition: background 0.15s ease; }
.quote-signed-cta:hover { background: #2AB5A0; }
.quote-dark .quote-signed--closed { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
.quote-dark .quote-signed-title, .quote-dark .quote-signed-label { color: #fff; }
.quote-dark .quote-signed-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
.quote-dark .quote-signed-cta { background: #fff; color: #1a1a1a; }
.quote-dark .quote-signed-cta:hover { background: #2AB5A0; color: #fff; }

/* ─── Client ─── */
.quote-client { padding: 24px 40px; }
.quote-client-label { font-size: 0.625rem; font-weight: 600; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.quote-client-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; }
